Package game.utils

Class RuneManager

java.lang.Object
game.utils.RuneManager
public class RuneManager extends Object
A RuneManager class which modifies and manages the Runes. In this case it will be used to add or subtract the runeCount of the Runes object. Created by:
Version:
1.0
